<br />
<br />Do you know what NP did call the discrete logic? Or did they not mention discrete for the MMC campaign?
<br />
<br />Would official programming documentation be welcomed at NesDev if it were hunted down? (BTW, is NesDev the correct capitalization or is it NESdev like the forum on this board?)
<br />
<br />
<br />Edit: Direction = directional

		

